title: Tom Daley Goes Global S01E01 Thailand PDTV x264 TM mp4
description:
Tom Daley Goes Global follows the adventures of Tom Daley as he takes part in a whistle-stop backpacking trip. He is joined by his best friend Sophie as they visit different countries including countries Thailand, Japan, Australia, Morocco and New Zealand.

Season 1, Episode 01 - Thailand
In Thailand, Tom and Sophie want to take part in a skydive, but they have arrived during monsoon season so might not even get into the sky. Tom struggles to be traveling alone for the first time, especially with the accommodation and hole in the floor toilets on a sleeper train.
